node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Andrew Marttila on July 16, 2021 tagging @kittenxlady. May be an image of cat.

node.text:
This little dude gave us a real scare last night. I stayed up with him late to make sure he continued to eat and drink, and that he didn’t fade away. With some medical treatment and TLC, he’s looking much more chipper today. Fingers crossed he’s able to combat this infection. 

This is really hard. Every time I look at him I have to hold back tears. I know how this story ends, I just hope there are many more chapters before we get there. ❤️

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Andrew Marttila on July 15, 2021 tagging @kittenxlady, @orphankittenclub, and @saratoga_cat_sanctuary. May be an image of 1 person, cat and indoor.

node.text:
My new gf 🥰

She’s got a rotund belly, crunchy meatface, and a huge bald spot on her head. Could she be any more perfect?
